What you need to know:

Bears, who had again used their home advantage to stun Italians Dinamo Sassari 93-71 last month, were inspired by American QJ Peterson who scored a game-high 35 points, seven rebounds and five assistsKenyan international small forward Ongwae got the Bears off to a nice start after scoring a two-pointer and a lay-up for 4-0Bears have to beat Tenerife in their last group match on January 20 at Aarhus Arena to boost their chances of advancing to the play-offs